{"word":"δωρεά","slug":"δωρεά","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δωρεά</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a gift, present</i>, <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> <i>a free gift, bounty</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>beneficium</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <el>δωρεάν</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <i>as a free gift, freely</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>gratis</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to no purpose, in vain</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}